## Sprint 4 — Code Review Implementation

### Backend (BE)

**5 new API routes created:**

| Route | Method | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `api/pipelines/[id]/changes` | GET | List all code changes for a pipeline (via latest session) |
| `api/pipelines/[id]/changes/[changeId]` | GET | Single change with full diff/content |
| `api/pipelines/[id]/changes/[changeId]/review` | PATCH | Approve / request-changes / reject with optional comment |
| `api/pipelines/[id]/changes/[changeId]/comments` | GET/POST | Line-level comments (graceful fallback if table missing) |
| `api/pipelines/[id]/review/approve-all` | POST | Bulk approve all pending changes |

**Utility: `src/lib/review/handle-review-result.ts`**
- After any review action, checks all changes: if all approved → pipeline `completed`, if any rejected → pipeline `failed`.

### Frontend (FE)

**5 new components in `src/components/review/`:**

- **`file-tree.tsx`** — Sidebar file list with change-type icons (+/-/edit), review status badges, and active highlight
- **`review-summary.tsx`** — Progress bar + counters (total/approved/pending/rejected/changes-requested) + total +/- lines
- **`diff-viewer.tsx`** — Unified and split diff views using `parsePatch` from `diff` package, regex syntax highlighting for TS/JS/SQL, hover-to-comment per line
- **`line-comment.tsx`** — Popover component for viewing/adding line-level comments
- **`review-actions.tsx`** — Approve (green) / Request Changes (yellow, with comment input) / Reject (red, with AlertDialog confirmation)

**Updated `src/app/(dashboard)/pipelines/[id]/review/page.tsx`:**
- Full layout: header with unified/split toggle → sidebar (summary + file tree + bulk approve) + main (diff viewer + review actions + inline comment panel)
- `tsc --noEmit` → 0 errors, `eslint --fix` → 0 errors/warnings
